"built in the form of an"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azaj","text_ar":"اَزَج"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not closed in the front,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"face:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M, Msb: *) [and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a palace;"},{"kind":"text","text":"often used in this sense in Arabic as well as in Persian: and in the present day, the former, and more commonly"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liywaAn","text_ar":"لِيوَان"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is Persian, is also applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an estrade; a slightly-raised portion of the floor, generally extending nearly from the door to the end,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to each end, of a room:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] pl. of the former,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awaAwiynu","text_ar":"اَوَاوِينُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, K,) because the sing. is originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iwowaAnN","text_ar":"اـِوْوَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iywaAnaAtN","text_ar":"اـِيوَانَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and pl. of the latter,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uwnN","text_ar":"اُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T, S, K.) Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iywaAnu kisoraY","text_ar":"اـِيوَانُ كِسْرَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The great porch,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the palace, of Kisrà,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Chosroes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"who is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAHibu AlA_iywaAni","text_ar":"صَاحِبُ الاـِيوَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (T, S, Msb.) ―         -b2-  Also the latter, [and app., accord. to the Msb, the former also,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Any prop,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"support,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing: (T, Msb:) particularly,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a pole of a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tent of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xibaA='","text_ar":"خِبَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T.) ―         -b3-  The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iywaAn","text_ar":"اـِيوَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lijaAm","text_ar":"لِجَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"[is The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"headstall of the bridle;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and] has for its pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iywaAnaAtN","text_ar":"اـِيوَانَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T, K.)"}],"source_refs":["T","S","M","Msb","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%A5%D9%8A%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%86/","headword_ar":"إيوان","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_32","lexicon_en":"Supplément aux dictionnaires arabes by Reinhart Dozy (d. 1883 CE)","lexicon_ar":"تكملة المعاجم العربية لرينهارت دوزي","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=49927#e6388e","body_html":"إيوان: يذكر ويؤنث (انظر معجم ابن بدرون) - ولجام إيوان، انظر ابن العوام 2: 595."}]}}